			"relativePublishTimeDescription": "Изменено 4 года назад",
			"rating": 5,
			"text": {
				"text": "Very efficient and quick. I got a PCR test done for travel purposes at 11h30 and received my result via e-mail later the same day at 16h00. Not a problem to queue for about 30min. Just be prepared to queue in sun which at 38 degrees celcuis gets a bit hot after a while.",
